CustomField.formula: IF( NOT(ISBLANK(Overridden_Membership_Start_Date__c)), Overridden_Membership_Start_Date__c, IF( AND( ISBLANK(Overridden_Membership_Start_Date__c), Initial_Payment_Date__c >= Agreement_Date__c ), Initial_Payment_Date__c, IF( AND( ISBLANK(Overridden_Membership_Start_Date__c), Initial_Payment_Date__c < Agreement_Date__c ), Agreement_Date__c, NULL)))
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Calculates the later of Initial Payment Date and Agreement Date
CustomField.label: Membership Start Date
